quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  112,1,"Tharowangka: Sukaniyan so Allah, a isa isa!"
  112,2,"So Allah a Puphangangaron­ganan!"
  112,3,"Da Mbawata, go da Mbawata­an,"
  112,4,"Go da-a Miya-adun a saginda Niyan a isa bo."
  113,1,"Tharowangka: A Mulindong Ako ko Kadnan o khapita,"
  113,2,"Po-on ko karat-an o nganin a Inadun Niyan,"
  113,3,"Go so karata-an o Gagawi-i igira-a Miyakalibotung,"
  113,4,"Go so karata-an o Puphaman­giyop ko manga palot,"
  113,5,"Go so karata-an o makasi-ig igira-a miyani-ig."
  114,1,"Tharowangka: A Mulindong Ako ko Kadnan o manga Mano­siya,"
  114,2,"A Phapa-ar ko manga Mano­siya,"
  114,3,"A Tohan o manga Manosiya,"
  114,4,"Po-on ko karata-an o Puphan­gonsi, a Puphano-o so-ok,-"
  114,5,"So Puphangonsi ko manga rarub o manga Manosiya,-"
  114,6,"A pud ko manga Jinn, a go so manga Manosiya."